{"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshotter\/addannotation:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter\/addAnnotation:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Adds an annotation to the snapshotter."}],"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter"]]},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Method","symbolKind":"method","title":"addAnnotation:","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"addAnnotation:"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"addAnnotation:"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapSnapshotter(im)addAnnotation:"},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"addAnnotation:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:Qoobjc(pl)MLNAnnotation","text":"id<MLNAnnotation>"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"annotation"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"annotation","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The annotation object to add to the receiver. This object"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"must conform to the "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol. The snapshotter retains the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"annotation object."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":""},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline"},{"type":"text","text":", and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointCollection"},{"type":"text","text":" objects cannot be added to the snapshotter at this time."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Any multipoint, multipolyline, multipolygon, shape or point collection"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object that is specified is silently ignored."}]}],"name":"Note","type":"aside","style":"note"}]}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapSnapshotter":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapSnapshotter"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter"},{"type":"text","text":" generates static raster images of the map. Each snapshot"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"image depicts a portion of a map defined by an "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotOptions"},{"type":"text","text":" object"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"you provide. The snapshotter generates an "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshot"},{"type":"text","text":" object"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"asynchronously, calling "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" methods if defined, then"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"passing it into a completion handler once tiles and other resources needed for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the snapshot are finished loading."}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshotter","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","title":"MLNMapSnapshotter"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNPointCollection":{"title":"MLNPointCollection","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointCollection","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointCollection","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object represents a shape consisting of one or more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"disconnected vertices, specified as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CLLocationCoordinate2D"},{"type":"text","text":" instances. The"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"points in the collection may be related but are not connected spatially. For"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"example, you could use a point collection to represent all the trees in an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"orchard."}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNPointCollection"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpointcollection"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNPolyline":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline","title":"MLNPolyline","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpolyline","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNPolyline"}],"type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline"},{"type":"text","text":" object represents a shape consisting of two or more vertices,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"specified as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CLLocationCoordinate2D"},{"type":"text","text":" instances, and the line segments that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"connect them. For example, you could use an polyline to represent a road or the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"path along which something moves."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapSnapshotter/addAnnotation:":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"addAnnotation:"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter\/addAnnotation:","title":"addAnnotation:","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshotter\/addannotation:","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Adds an annotation to the snapshotter."}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"addAnnotation:"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Optional methods about significant events when creating a snapshot using an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter"},{"type":"text","text":" object."}],"fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshotterdelegate","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate","title":"MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","title":"MLNAnnotation","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotation"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapSnapshotOptions":{"title":"MLNMapSnapshotOptions","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The options to use when creating images with the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotOptions","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapSnapshotOptions"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshotoptions","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"title":"MapLibre","role":"collection","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMultiPolyline":{"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipolyline","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMultiPolyline"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object represents a shape consisting of one or more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"polylines. For example, you could use a multipolyline shape to represent both"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"sides of a divided highway (dual carriageway), excluding the median (central"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"reservation): each carriageway would be a distinct "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline","title":"MLNMultiPolyline","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapSnapshot":{"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapSnapshot"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","title":"MLNMapSnapshot","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshot","abstract":[{"text":"An image generated by a snapshotter object.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshot"}}}